---
// src/components/ThemeSelect.astro
//
// Override Starlight's default <ThemeSelect> component with a no-op.
//
// The Codex is committed to dark-only theming - light mode is not supported
// and the theme palette is hue-rotated via PaletteTuner instead. Removing
// the dark/light switcher from the top-right header simplifies the UI and
// reclaims real estate.
//
// Register in astro.config.mjs:
//
//   starlight({
//     components: {
//       ThemeSelect: './src/components/ThemeSelect.astro',
//     },
//   })
//
// This file deliberately renders nothing. If you want to restore the
// theme switcher later, simply remove the ThemeSelect line from
// astro.config.mjs and delete this file.
---

{/* intentionally empty - no theme switcher in dark-only mode */}
